Go to
HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Siuf\Rules
and change the DWORD strings
NumberOfSIUFInPeriod
PeriodInNanoSeconds
both to
0

&

Go to
HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Assistance\Client\1.0\Settings
and change the DWORD string
ImplicitFeedback
to
0


Finish. No restart required. You can config this in Windows privacy settings too.
